  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ORB Agent + IA + Telegram\n\n1. Webhook `orb-globalsend` recebe POST do harness\n2. Filtra `app=orb-agent`\n3. `setup_found` → OpenAI revisa contexto ORB\n4. Telegram alerta (approve/reject/review)\n5. `paper_alert` → Telegram SL/TP paper\n6. Resposta JSON ao harness\n\n**Após importar:**\n- Credencial **OpenAI** no nó OpenAI Review\n- Credencial **Telegram** nos nós Telegram\n- Chat ID em cada nó Telegram\n- Atualizar `.env`: `ORB_WEBHOOK_URL=https://8.fullscopetrade.com/webhook/orb-globalsend`\n- Testar: `python scripts/test-webhook.py`\n- **Ativar** workflow\n\nVer `docs/deploy-n8n.md`",
        "height": 400,
        "width": 460
      },
